{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "b2d14546-9963-40e4-98b6-ee98e741ad72",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 2 04 - Runes 2",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "f4072ea6-fabd-4732-bcdb-86a449146db7",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "b3407631-8110-42d4-92be-668495090797",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "ad2bd191-5f8a-4ba9-8a9e-ef4bba83d497",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This lesson will be a lecture on runes and runestones. You've already constructed and enchanted two types of runestones - personal and combat. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "3b421269-1980-4c6a-903b-d11c4a4a9393",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Of course, these are not the technical terms for the types of runestones. I just believe that \"Personal\" and \"Combat\" are easier for you to remember than \"Imperum\" and \"Responsum\" runestones.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "403c077f-48e8-449f-b8eb-49549dea3052",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Personal runestones are held in the hand and invoked with a command to cast the spell; Combat runestones are placed upon the ground, invoked with a command, but the spell is not cast until something else draws near to the runestone.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f34d1085-3f3f-4b1a-909c-74fe5d036759",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Over the next few days, you will learn the runes and make the runestones for three different spells - Sol, Claustra, and Null. These can be of great use in combat against Undead or hostile magic.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e27eff42-7072-478c-b6f9-a7c6b504e028",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before I get further into this lecture?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "2c2c2a0e-bd9d-4e33-8227-b4dae14b8251",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "bb31cc3f-00e1-44fc-bf72-efb0f1dc25d9",
                            "text": "Ask About the Professor's Past",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c36fdcd6-0a7c-466b-a538-824adaf21e40",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "How did you get to be a Wizard? Did you just go to Wizard school?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0daa1830-0250-41ea-a7b2-3fe1b1e02acb",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Oh, no. After I manifested my magical ability, I was hired by a Magic User to keep house for him and do light spellcasting. He was reclusive, clutchpursed, and surly. Most servants couldn't stand to work for him.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c9b2ed93-bcb9-4395-b664-bcf072079322",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "From him, I learned to enchant charms and periapts to sell to wealthy nobles. Of course, given my Master's personality, I was the one to do most of the selling.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e67bcb0f-2c6e-478e-a047-607e46fd07a1",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "One day while I was endeavoring to sell an amulet to Baronet Fitzgerald of Southumbria, I met two extraordinary Magic Users who were visiting the barony. I got into a magical discussion with them, and they were impressed with my magical knowledge and ability",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "37a9d0c8-cf7c-45e7-9414-0824fcf8d7e2",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Archmagus Erasmus and Fenrus became my sponsors at the Wizard's Institute of Technocery, That's where I became a Wizard.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f021bd7a-6163-4698-aada-90792898b825",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "The moral of my digression is that even the most unlikely of people can become Magic Users and Wizards.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "fd53327f-5925-4bde-9f2a-33311193c87a",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "62",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "7b023c24-12da-49ec-bbb6-ab0755a43d11",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "12",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "2a5bd486-f07e-4e35-b4b3-4ed0951bed33",
                            "text": "Ask About Runestones",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e5db1a06-a0e0-4b3e-9428-d81aee51e169",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Are there only two types of runestones? It seems like there should be more...",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "68818b23-057f-4c92-9933-fd8fa37c7969",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "You are correct, Mr. O'Conner. There are more classifications for runestones than just those two. Initium runestones, for example, can be placed anywhere and require a command word to activate.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b4be5e47-d507-4ecd-8e13-6989ab26e70a",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "We can easily devote an entire elective session to runestones. However, this elective is merely an overview, so we will not be going into such detail.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "e72df304-c860-4f98-b32c-ac473070e893",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "62",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "987e97a4-3be0-430f-957b-372ba014a9cf",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "6d9ebb47-dd3e-49f4-a4a9-17f8c4b92eae",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky About Wizards and Big Words",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "29ea370c-599c-46f0-bc8c-cc06c3bf3580",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Is it true that Wizards never use a short word when a longer word can do? ",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "556d393f-5e71-4df5-b808-6026df5cce86",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That is a misunderstand of the way Wizards view words and symbols. We prefer to use the most precise words with which to communicate. Therefore, our vocabulary gives the impression of being obscure to the uninitiated.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "f729a4c5-5111-496d-8ad6-20becd9bcb3e",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "62",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "f6e89564-0717-4274-b33b-259bfce384ba",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "1",
                                                "change": "0",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "5682b871-19dd-41c6-b821-7dc4e23d1548",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
